Package: Friedman
Title: Tools for Exploring and Visualizing Data Mining Results
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Zara", "Gonzalez", email = "zaragonzalez@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides helper functions for cleaning, summarizing,
    and visualizing data mining and statistical analysis results.
    The package is designed to support student projects by organizing
    repeated workflows into reusable tools for analysis and reporting.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: ggplot2, dplyr
